// ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
//  Shared Conversation — included by all persona topics
//
//  Features:
//    • <bot name>     — persona-adaptive text
//    • <set>/<get>    — user language, name, mood, onboarded
//    • <formal>       — capitalize collected names
//    • @ redirect     — DRY trigger variants
//    • * conditions   — language-branched + onboarding gate
//    • ^ continue     — readable multi-line responses
//    • {weight=N}     — preferred greeting variants appear more often
//    • {random}       — inline emoji variety
//    • (@array)       — sentiment keyword matching
// ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

! local concat = newline

> topic conversation

  // ── Greetings (with onboarding gate) ───────────────────────
  // First-time users (onboarded undefined) → trigger onboarding.
  // Returning users with a known name get a personalised reply.

  + (bonjou|bonswa|salut|alo)
  * <get onboarded> == undefined => <set lang=ht>{topic=onboarding}Bonjou! Anvan nou kòmanse...
  * <get welcomed> == true => <set lang=ht>👋 Bienveni tounen, <get name>! Kisa w bezwen jodi a?{weight=3}
  - <set lang=ht>👋 Bonjou! Byenveni nan <bot name>. Kisa w bezwen jodi a?{weight=3}
  - <set lang=ht>🌟 Salut! Byenveni nan <bot name>. Tape *help* pou wè koman m ka ede w.{weight=2}
  - <set lang=ht>{random}👋|🌟|✨{/random} Bonjou! Mwen la pou ede w. Kisa w bezwen?

  + (hello|hi|hey)
  * <get onboarded> == undefined => <set lang=en>{topic=onboarding}Hello! Before we start...
  * <get welcomed> == true => <set lang=en>👋 Welcome back, <get name>! What can I help you with?{weight=3}
  * <get lang> == ht => <set lang=ht>👋 Bonjou! Byenveni nan <bot name>. Kisa w bezwen jodi a?
  - <set lang=en>👋 Hello! Welcome to <bot name>. What can I help you with today?{weight=3}
  - <set lang=en>🌟 Hi there! Welcome to <bot name>. Type *help* to see what I can do.{weight=2}
  - <set lang=en>{random}👋|🌟|✨{/random} Hey! I'm here to help. What do you need?

  // ── How Are You ────────────────────────────────────────────
  + (koman ou ye|how are you|sa k ap fet|sa kap fet)
  * <get lang> == en => I'm doing well, thanks! 😊 How can I help you today?
  - Mwen byen, mèsi! 😊 Kijan m ka ede w jodi a?

  // ── Thanks ─────────────────────────────────────────────────
  + (mesi|merci|thanks|thank) *
  * <get lang> == en => You're welcome! {random}😊|🙏|👍{/random} Type *help* if you need anything else.
  - Avèk plezi! {random}😊|🙏|👍{/random} Tape *help* si w bezwen lòt bagay.

  + (mesi|merci|thanks|thank)
  * <get lang> == en => You're welcome! {random}😊|🙏|👍{/random} Type *help* if you need anything else.
  - Avèk plezi! {random}😊|🙏|👍{/random} Tape *help* si w bezwen lòt bagay.

  // ── Farewell ───────────────────────────────────────────────
  + (orevwa|bye|goodbye|kenbe|babay|adye) *
  * <get lang> == en => <set topic=random>Goodbye! {random}👋|🌟|✌️{/random} Don't hesitate to come back.
  - <set topic=random>Orevwa! Kenbe la {random}👋|🌟|✌️{/random} Pa ezite retounen si w bezwen èd.

  + (orevwa|bye|goodbye|kenbe|babay|adye)
  * <get lang> == en => <set topic=random>Goodbye! Have a great day {random}🌟|☀️|🙌{/random}
  - <set topic=random>Babay! Pase yon bon jounen {random}🌟|☀️|🙌{/random}

  // ── Sentiment Detection ────────────────────────────────────
  // Catch frustration/positivity keywords anywhere in message.
  // Sets mood var, included in AI context for tone adaptation.

  + [*] (@frustration) [*]
  * <get lang> == en => <set mood=frustrated>😔 I understand you're frustrated. Let me try to help better.
  ^ Type *help* to see what I can do, or describe your issue and I'll do my best.
  - <set mood=frustrated>😔 Mwen konprann ou fristré. Kite m eseye ede w pi byen.
  ^ Tape *help* pou wè opsyon yo, oswa eksplike pwoblèm ou an epi m ap fè sa m kapab.

  + [*] (@positive) [*]
  * <get lang> == en => <set mood=happy>😊 Great to hear! What can I help you with?
  - <set mood=happy>😊 Kontan tande sa! Kisa m ka fè pou ou?

  // ── Persona Switching ────────────────────────────────────────
  // "pale ak vant" / "talk to sales" → gateway re-routes to new persona.
  // The {{persona_switch}} sentinel is intercepted by engine.py.

  + [*] (pale ak|talk to) (vant|sales) [*]
  * <get lang> == en => <set switch_persona=konex-sales>{{persona_switch}}
  - <set switch_persona=konex-sales>{{persona_switch}}

  + [*] (pale ak|talk to) (sipò|support|teknik) [*]
  * <get lang> == en => <set switch_persona=konex-support>{{persona_switch}}
  - <set switch_persona=konex-support>{{persona_switch}}

  + [*] (pale ak|talk to) (talkprep|coach|preparation|preparasyon) [*]
  * <get lang> == en => <set switch_persona=talkprep>{{persona_switch}}
  - <set switch_persona=talkprep>{{persona_switch}}

  // ── Capabilities (redirects to persona-specific help) ─────
  + (what can you do|what ou ka do|kisa ou ka do)
  @ help

< topic
